Pre-Game Insights: India and Canada will play against each other for the first-time in the T20I format during the T20 World Cup 2024.
India has qualified for the Super 8 stage of the tournament, while Canada is looking to stay in the hunt for the Super 8 spot.
Others: The match will take place on June 15, 2024, at 8:00 PM IST at Central Broward Regional Park Stadium, Lauderhill.
